flowchart TD
    A[Application] --> W[Workflow Service]

    W --> K[Knowledge Service]
    W --> G[Geometry Service]
    W --> V[Validation Service]
    W --> E[Export Service]

    K --> KP[Knowledge Port]
    G --> GP[Geometry Port]
    V --> VP[Validation Dependencies]
    E --> EP[Export Port]

    GP --> GK[Geometry Kernel]
    EP --> EA[Export Adapter]
    KP --> KA[Knowledge Adapter]

    W --> EB[Event Bus Port]
    EB --> EBA[Event Bus Adapter]
